<figure type="diagram"> 
<p>*uCowslips Primroses MalePlants. Tube of corolla long, throat short— Stamens long— pollen in water about <formula><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>6000</mn></mfrac></math></formula> of inch in diameter. Pistil short, stigma far beneath anthers,— surface of stigma smoother Female plants:— Tube of corolla short, throat long.— Stamens short, pollen in water about <formula><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>6</mn><mn>6000</mn></mfrac></math></formula> of in inch in diameter.—<ref target="#foot.f3"/> Pistil long, stigma far above anthers, surface of stigma rougher.—</p> </figure> 
